 9[f] "survey" means the survey of a 7[mechanically propelled vessel] under this Act; 
 9[g] "surveyor" means a surveyor appointed under this Act; and 
 10[ga "tidal water" has the meaning assigned to it in clause (49) of section 3 of the Merchant Shipping Act, 1958 (44 of 1958);] 
 9[h] "voyage" includes the plying of a 7[mechanically propelled vessel] at or about any place. 


